article_title: Texas, Houston physician leaders seek increased health access
article_text:
Texas, Houston physician leaders seek increased health access

Photo: Gary Fountain, For The Chronicle Dr. Elizabeth Torres, president of the Harris County Medical...

Leaders of political organizations representing state and local physicians Tuesday said Texas lawmakers must increase the number of medical residency positions they finance to keep doctors in the state to treat its growing population.
